title: Index of Truck Tonnage for General Freight Carriers for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, Quarterly, 1946-1960 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, Monthly, 1955-1964. Source: U.S. Bureau Of The Census; Originally From The American Trucking Association, Department Of Research And Transport Economics.
